  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Offered on a half board basis, the Hotel Ily has breakfast and dinner included. </p>
<p>Fuel up for a day of adventures at the lovely breakfast buffet which includes a classic continental breakfast offering and a range of additional hot options. </p>
<p>A three course evening meal is served in the hotels restaurant, Le Bonami. The menu varies, however fresh and local produce is used to create hearty winter dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The House of Happiness - the Hotel Ily is a modern hotel set in the Eucherts area of <a data-udi="umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c93b881bd494483871697b278b37899}" title="La Rosiere">La Rosiere</a>. The warm wood and stylish decor combined with a luxury spa, hearty food and amazing views of the valley certainly ticks all the boxes for a relaxing ski holiday in France. </p>
<p>The rooms all feature natural and bright decor, with most of the rooms having balconies to take in the view and pure mountain air. There are generous sized Family Suites and some interconnecting rooms, making the hotel a good choice for families and groups.</p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>The large bar and lounge area is a perfect spot to relax after a full day on the slopes. C<span>hoose from sitting on the sunny south-facing terrace and soak up the sunshine or admire the sunset, or </span>cosy up in front of the warm fireplace  - If you fancy a sweet treat after skiing, ''The Break'' serves delicious hot chocolate and cake until 5pm. When its dinner time, you can enjoy a varied three course evening meal often including comforting winter dishes made with local produce.</p>
<h2>Wellness and rejuvenation</h2>
<p>After a day on the slopes make the most of the luxury spa, it has gorgeous views of the mountains and is the perfect place to relax. The spa area features an indoor swimming pool, an outdoor hot tub and two indoor hot tubs, sauna, relaxation area and steam room. And new for this winter there is a well equipped fitness room with NOHRD brand equipment including bikes, mats, benches, dumbbells and rowing machines. </p>
<h2>Family friendly </h2>
<p>Hotel Ily has a kids club during school holidays for the little ones between four and twelve, letting you make full use of the spa and bar areas. The club runs in the evening, and includes games, film screenings and a kids playroom.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
