  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Mountain View Rooms</strong> can sleep up to two people and are around 25-29<span>m². These rooms can be made up as a twin or double, and have a balcony with great views of the Alps.</span><span> These rooms are also available for sole occupancy, please call our Reservations team a call to book.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Family Suites</strong> can sleep up to six people and are around 58m². These rooms have </span><span>two bedrooms, one with a double bed and the second with bunk beds. There is a lounge area with a sofa bed when needed,  suitable for two children or one adult, and two bathrooms.</span><span></span><span></span></p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span>All bedrooms can be made up as a twin or double bed (please specify your preference when booking)</span></li>
<li><span>Satellite TV</span></li>
<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>
<li><span>Tea and coffee facilities</span></li>
<li><span>Bathrobe and slippers</span></li>
<li><span>Mini-fridge </span></li>
<li><span>Safe</span></li>
<li><span>Bath with shower head attachment</span></li>
<li>Underfloor<span> heating</span></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
